  { includes/cabrel132_2.i }  

  OUTPUT STREAM str_2 TO VALUE(aux_nmarqimp) PAGED PAGE-SIZE 84.

  VIEW STREAM str_2 FRAME f_cabrel132_2.

  /** Gerar arquivo de solicitacao de cartao de credito **/
  FOR EACH tt-crawcrd 
      BREAK BY tt-crawcrd.cdadmcrd
